c=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjaKRUf.png&h=92dbab44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9437sD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9437sD.png&h=b8aba9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kxmuizo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxmuizo.png&h=be699882&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"第2張示意圖畫到好似想錫佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27715bdf13884724967a753ae2ce7307d533e8c0","tid":946234,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"234d6672ce7393fb9426aa33a15b6ae6575a31c3","tid":946234,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<br />\n啲仆街煙民<br />\n食煙死埋一面又唔係唔畀食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1e29a8a5469fe58c353a24ce8d6d6c747bb2e2","tid":946234,"uid":197857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"其實最on9既地方係還拖就變毆鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊衰"},{"pid":"c5a112cfe6dc54e0c3bf8103749551b2dc846436","tid":946234,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"幾多年前"},{"pid":"de65e85d5d019d0b37bcd3fb8b2ca8c3bec03e2b","tid":946234,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"事主稱：「當時好多人睇到我俾人打，我叫佢哋幫手做證人，個個都話趕時間返工拒絕。」更有人冷漠稱：「你唔好阻住架小巴走啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返工不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b950b960afa57420853f0e33ef015814262ac4","tid":946234,"uid":226346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:23:05.000Z","msg":"香港地阻人搵食燒春袋架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42395cf0f3b0e368b7ff902452f55953ec